        "message": "LU-19237 ldiskfs: drop outdated i_version configure check\n\ni_version was introduced ages ago, in 4.14-rc1 e462ec50cb5fa\nwe can see MS_I_VERSION is being renamed to SB_I_VERSION, and\nthat is already before the cutoff for our current 4.18 support\n(rhel8), so we can drop the check.\n\nChange-Id: I4cad806e6f2a972651d165199e73650bd808a0be\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/60562\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\n"
